Class TimeWindowFilter

java.lang.Object
  vista.set.TimeWindowFilter
All Implemented Interfaces:
Predicate<DataReference>
public class TimeWindowFilter
extends java.lang.Object
implements Predicate<DataReference>

Filters given data reference using its time window. A data reference is acceptable if its time window contains the time window in this filter.
